14 SUMMARY
1155 This amendment updates the date on which the review and report of the Department of
1166 Administrative and Financial Services required by the bill on the provisions of the law that
1177 refer to Maine income tax are due. The amendment exempts taxpayers without reportable
1188 tax liability from filing a Maine income tax return and eliminates individual Maine income
1199 tax credits. The amendment also adds an appropriations and allocations section.
